<h1 id="changes-to-etcsshsshd_config">Changes to /etc/ssh/sshd_config</h1>
<pre><code>Protocol 2
AllowUsers alice bob
PermitRootLogin no
</code></pre>

<h1 id="changes-to-iptables">Changes to iptables</h1>
<pre><code>iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --dport 22 -m state --state NEW -m recent --set --name ssh --rsource
iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --dport 22 -m state --state NEW -m recent ! --rcheck --seconds 60 --hitcount 4 --name ssh --rsource -j ACCEPT
</code></pre>

